fieldData.T16l_projects_NOTES||id_note|::Text: Email sent to alex@itis.com.au (Mickey Spillane)The email ID is 135Dear Mickey,Please find attached new referral from Employers Mutual in the matter of . Upon receipt of this email, please acknowledge receipt to ma@ma-investigations.com.auOur Ref: PRJ00001Due date to client: <<Date Due>>Update to client: 07/06/2017According to our clients Charge Out Centres - it appears that the charge out for this file will be ????. NOTE: Photos are required for all Employers Mutual files.Please note the following requirements of Employers Mutual:Witness details* EM have instructed that personal contact details for witnesses NOT be included in either their statement or our report. Addresses should be Cl- the employer.* EM requires us to still obtain personal address and contact details, and these are to be recorded using the attached file note. This note will be kept in our file only and will not be returned with our report. Do not include the Witness Details file note as an attachment to your report.* Please find attached EM's statement template.Service standards• Service standards for Employers Mutual are attached and require 100% compliance.• EM requires first phone calls to be made within 24 hours of receipt in our office, by the investigator. • Upon receipt of instructions, please phone the claims officer to discuss investigation requirements.• If contact cannot be made with the claimant or insured following 3 consecutive days, please phone the claims officer to discuss alternatives.* If you are unable to contact the claims officer, please let us know.* EM require an update within 5 working days. As such, please email a brief update to claire@mainvestigations.com.au in the required format by the above nominated update date.Report* Please find attached EM's report template. Travel* Should travel exceed 1 hour each way we will require EM's approval, prior to departure. As such, please contact me so that I can make the necessary arrangements.* Travel is calculated from applicable charge out centre.Please ensure all laws, client SLA's and company Policies are complied with when conducting your investigation. If you have any queries or expect any delays, please contact me.Kind regards
